HEADWORD: Provisorily
<hw>Pro*vi"so*ri*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a
provisory manner; conditionally; subject to a proviso; <as>as, to admit
a doctrine <ex>provisorily</ex></as>.</def> <rj><au>Sir W.
